headline: CTI CRYOGENICS FREQUENCY CONVERTER
description:
Frequency Converter 
New--Never Used    Allows CTI-CRYOGENICS equipment to operate efficiently when connected to a supply voltage with a line frequency of 50Hz.  The Frequency Converter is designed for use with CTI-CRYOGENICS 9600, 8200, 8510, 8500, and 1020R compressors, and On-Board and Cryo-Torr Cryopumps.
